summary: This code imports pstats module, creates a Stats object from 'profile.bin' file, filters and sorts the stats, then prints the resulting statistics.

details.comment: This code imports pstats module, creates a Stats object from 'profile.bin' file, filters and sorts the stats, then prints the resulting statistics.
details.content:
import pstats
# from pstats import SortKey
p = pstats.Stats('profile.bin')
stats = p.strip_dirs().sort_stats(2)
stats.print_stats()
